modName: War Hero Stormcloak - The Battle for Fort Sungard save
summary: Save game for the steam "War Hero" achievement.
descriptionHtml:
Here is my save file starting at the beginning of the quest "The Battle for Fort Sungard". You will have to travel to the quest destination yourself. You will have some gold and a skill point to spend.
You might want to clean the save because the mods I use may be incompatible with those you are using. This may cause errors.
Place the save in DocumentsMy Games/skyrim/saves
author: Nydhoggr
